{"tid":2082403,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Project Winter》5-8人 合作與背叛 雪山倖存＋狼人殺","createTime":"2020-06-28T04:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T16:06:02.000Z","uid":152776,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"75331c0b2443ac849e98a2a119b5d67d42542f44","tid":2082403,"uid":152776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbX2a72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbX2a72.jpg&h=803bf2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPC Game，5-8位玩家合作喺雪地逃生<br />\n遊戲中玩家們被困喺雪地木屋，要搵人求救<br />\n但發電機壞咗，大家要合作做任務整返好佢<br />\n<br />\n各人會肚餓同凍，要定時食嘢同生火／返入木屋取暖<br />\n肚餓可以搵野果、殺動物整肉，甚至食人（其他玩家）<br />\n<br />\n有1~2個玩家係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>背叛者</strong></span>，要暗中殺晒所有人，或拖時間<br />\n可以整陷阱、落毒、開槍、用刀偷襲或直接用拳頭打死等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dUxEXRN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdUxEXRN.png&h=e6de05a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最正係佢個語音系統, 隻Game一定要開Mic先好玩<br />\n得附近嘅人先聽到自己講嘢、越遠越細聲<br />\n例如你同另一個人出咗去搵資源，佢突然變臉想殺你<br />\n如果其他隊友太遠, 就算你叫救命都冇人聽到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9nc9ADL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9nc9ADL.jpg&h=24f4fb94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非整咗對講機, 先可以同遠方嘅人通話<br />\n壞人殺咗人，返到木屋又要講大話，向其他人作故仔<br />\n話另一個人比，狼咬死咗之類，甚至屈第二個殺人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tu3wOYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTu3wOYz.jpg&h=f4bcba15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木屋喺成個地圖正中間，大家可以返入去取暖<br />\n喺屋入面唔可以攻擊其他人<br />\n玩家們可以喺木屋投票，趕人出屋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXfWfEu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXfWfEu.jpg&h=aa9f6a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5人局=1壞人，6至8人局=2壞人<br />\n2個壞人天生有壞人對講機<br />\n可以偷偷用對講機Channel傾下點害其他人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVVZXT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVVZXT8.jpg&h=22eaf433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲Trailer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xgBKpFjtvZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxgBKpFjtvZQ&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=d1c66a90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xgBKpFjtvZQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaW-e8UjRPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTaW-e8UjRPI&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=d072901f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaW-e8UjRPI</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東話遊戲介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i-v6UkFRpxo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di-v6UkFRpxo&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=7c8e934c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i-v6UkFRpxo</a><br />\n（有樣嘢片主講錯咗，隻Game會有1-2個壞人先啱）<br />\n<br />\nGame Play<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DdwvboypU2E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDdwvboypU2E&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=d59a4475\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DdwvboypU2E</a><br />\n<br />\nSteam 而家做緊特價！隻Game只係59蚊！<br />\n建議一次過買埋Blackout Bundle DLC，多個模式玩，加埋都只係72蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXm6CQ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXm6CQ4.png&h=9689a203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/774861/Project_Winter/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F774861%2FProject_Winter%2F&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=e37381bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/774861/Project_Winter/</a>"},{"pid":"85b2420540eb3e5315c5cbf6bee2e3b896067961","tid":2082403,"uid":152776,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"隻Game亞服暫時只得普通話場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲有興趣一齊玩香港場，可以喺度留個名<br />\n夠人開場，我會喺度放低房名同PW <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者可以加入TG Group，方便約戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/projectwinterhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fprojectwinterhk&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=57ce7334\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/projectwinterhk</a>"},{"pid":"776dbe64e9d6e48cc2dc51e61ad0fea0336fa104","tid":2082403,"uid":152776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"有興趣幫手撳個正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同推下Post <br />\n各位巴絲有問題可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc911b84b3d142b2cfdaabb1c5462e69ad16f0f","tid":2082403,"uid":152776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"喜歡荒野合作生存遊戲的玩家，今年 Steam 又有一款獨立遊戲即將上架，由獨立工作室 Other Ocean Interactive 開發的《冬日計畫》（Project Winter），是一款 8 人制線上多人生存遊戲，它跟其他同類型不一樣的是，這群生存者有一位「背叛者」。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftOwO9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftOwO9r.jpg&h=cd54b5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《冬日計畫》主打多人合作尋求資源，在嚴苛的環境與野生動物危險下力圖生存。只不過，本作特別添加了「背叛者」，試想想在你一邊砍樹的時候，隊友冷不防的從背後偷襲...<br />\n<br />\n玩家需要與一群陌生玩家合作，搜集資源，與野生動物戰鬥，完成一連串的任務，才能呼叫載具逃出生天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aH3s6V2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaH3s6V2.jpg&h=04d8d6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n背叛者初期也必須在隱藏自己的身份下與其他生還者合作，否則他自己也活不下來，但是由於玩家彼此都不曉得對方的真實身份，彼此不可能 100% 完全信任，因此在推派任務時的分工合作與溝通便相當重要，同時還得提防誰是背叛者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxxBfPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxxBfPX.jpg&h=7385f07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在多數生存遊戲中，嚴苛的自然環境往往是最大的挑戰，但大自然再怎麼險惡都不及人心的萬分之一，或許這就是《冬日計畫》想帶來的玩法與含意。"},{"pid":"c0ac5b3ba05dc63f141c1cb95c1343284ce5a195","tid":2082403,"uid":10637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"依d要同班識既friend玩先好玩"},{"pid":"dd6c7787ff6351801e820a04ff62379602507414","tid":2082403,"uid":152776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"上面篇介紹又係寫錯咗<br />\n隻Game唔只一位背叛者"},{"pid":"22537b705b6a9338a9ba4cec56cc4ff2ffe6858b","tid":2082403,"uid":152776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0ac5b3ba05dc63f141c1cb95c1343284ce5a195","tid":2082403,"uid":10637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"依d要同班識既friend玩先好玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"巴打一齊玩啦，玩完就做到朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecd0f6efb3cd27eed91072c59f0ba93090ce748","tid":2082403,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0ac5b3ba05dc63f141c1cb95c1343284ce5a195","tid":2082403,"uid":10637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"依d要同班識既friend玩先好玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n無FD又無Mic<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2fff1d9366259768f82cc031620331afc51865","tid":2082403,"uid":152776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eecd0f6efb3cd27eed91072c59f0ba93090ce748","tid":2082403,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0ac5b3ba05dc63f141c1cb95c1343284ce5a195","tid":2082403,"uid":10637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"依d要同班識既friend玩先好玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n無FD又無Mic<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:51:5